from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
numeric_features = ['Цена', 'Площадь участка', 'Площадь, кв.м', 'Стоимость, доллар США за 1 кв.м']


numeric_data = data[numeric_features]


num_clusters = 15


kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=num_clusters, random_state=42)
data['Price_Zone'] = kmeans.fit_predict(numeric_data)


for zone in range(num_clusters):
print(f'Ценовая зона {zone}:')
print(data[data['Price_Zone'] == zone][['Адрес', 'Цена', 'Price_Zone']])
print('\n' + '='*50 + '\n')

import numpy as np
import pandas as pd

data_selo = data[data['Местоположение'].str.contains('предгорье|пригород|дача|трасса|водоем', case=False, na=False)]
data_gorod = data[data['Местоположение'].str.contains('город', case=False, na=False)]


def generate_synthetic_data(original_data, num_rows_to_generate):
mean = original_data.mean()
std = original_data.std()
synthetic_data = np.random.normal(mean, std, num_rows_to_generate)
return synthetic_data


num_rows_selo = 30
synthetic_data_zone = generate_synthetic_data(zone_data['Цена'], num_rows_gorod_per_zone)
num_rows_gorod_per_zone = 15
num_zones = len(data_gorod['Price_Zone'].unique())

synthetic_data_gorod = pd.DataFrame()
for zone in range(num_zones):
zone_data = data_gorod[data_gorod['Price_Zone'] == zone]
synthetic_data_zone = generate_synthetic_data(zone_data['Цена'], num_rows_gorod_per_zone)
synthetic_data_gorod = pd.concat([synthetic_data_gorod, pd.DataFrame({'Цена': synthetic_data_zone, 'Price_Zone': [zone]*num_rows_gorod_per_zone})])


final_data = pd.concat([data_selo, synthetic_data_selo, data_gorod, synthetic_data_gorod])
final_data
